WEBVTT

00:02.370 --> 00:04.472
MY OLD DRILL SERGEANT--
GUYS CALLED HIM CROCKETT...

00:04.505 --> 00:06.507
ON ACCOUNT OF THIS
COONSKIN CAP HE ALWAYS WORE.

00:06.540 --> 00:10.144
HE'D ALWAYS SAY IF HIS GUYS
WALKED INTO AN AMBUSH,
HIS PLATOON COMING UNDER FIRE,

00:10.178 --> 00:14.915
THE FIRST THING HE'D DO
IS PUT TWO BULLETS
RIGHT INTO HIS RADIO.

00:14.948 --> 00:18.319
OLD CROCKETT SAID
THE ACTUAL MOMENT...

00:18.352 --> 00:20.988
THAT HE ABSOLUTELY NEEDED
HIS RADIO TO CALL FOR BACKUP,

00:21.021 --> 00:23.691
THE DAMN THING SURE AS HELL
WOULDN'T WORK ANYWAY.

00:23.724 --> 00:26.026
AT LEAST THIS WAY,
HE'D KNOW WHY.

00:28.896 --> 00:31.565
GENTLEMEN.
[ Jonas ]
COLONEL.

00:33.134 --> 00:36.003
THE NEW DRUG MINISTER OF MEXICO
IS VISITING LOS ANGELES...

00:36.036 --> 00:38.572
TO ENGAGE IN HIGH-LEVEL TALKS
WITH THE D.E.A....

00:38.606 --> 00:40.874
OVER MIMOSAS AND SUCH.

00:40.908 --> 00:43.677
YOU WILL BE IN CHARGE
OF MR. SALAZAR'S PROTECTION
WHILE HE'S OUR GUEST.

00:43.711 --> 00:46.547
- SOUNDS LIKE A JOB
FOR THE SEALs.
- AND SO IT WOULD BE.

00:46.580 --> 00:49.083
BUT WE HAVE RELIABLE
INTELLIGENCE THAT
THE MEXICAN CARTEL...

00:49.117 --> 00:53.020
INTENDS TO ASSASSINATE
MR. SALAZAR WHILE
HE'S ON OUR SOIL.

00:53.053 --> 00:56.224
- A PROSPECT THE PRESIDENT
DOESN'T FIND APPEALING.
- WILL WE KNOW WHO TO LOOK FOR?

00:56.257 --> 00:58.559
CARTELS HAVE OUTSOURCED THE JOB
TO SOMEONE CODE-NAMED MONGOOSE.

00:58.592 --> 01:00.761
SPECULATION IS
HE'S PULLING THE STRINGS,
NOT THE TRIGGER.

01:00.794 --> 01:03.431
FULL INTELLIGENCE IS WAITING
FOR YOU IN THE TEAM BAY.

01:03.464 --> 01:06.334
I'LL BE IN D.C.
KAYLA WILL KEEP ME APPRISED.

01:10.671 --> 01:13.674
MACK, STAY BEHIND.

01:18.346 --> 01:21.949
[ Radio ]
* IT'S THE WEIGHT
OF THE WORLD *

01:21.982 --> 01:25.753
* COMIN' DOWN ON ME

01:25.786 --> 01:29.089
* IT'S THE WEIGHT
OF THE WORLD *

01:29.123 --> 01:32.059
* [ Stops ]
* [ Country On Radio ]

01:32.092 --> 01:35.829
HEY, HON.
YOU'RE HOME EARLY.
YEP.

01:35.863 --> 01:39.167
YOU TAKING INVENTORY,
OR ARE YOU GOING SOMEWHERE?

01:41.269 --> 01:43.404
- GOING HUNTING.
- WE WERE GOING TO
THE BEACH THIS WEEKEND.

01:43.437 --> 01:47.074
THE KIDS ARE WITH MY MOM.
THIS WAS OUR TIME.
I KNOW.

01:47.107 --> 01:49.143
YOU GOT SOMETHING
YOU WANNA TELL ME ABOUT?

01:49.177 --> 01:53.414
THE OLD MAN HAS ORDERED ME
TO GO AWAY FOR A LITTLE BIT,
AND THAT'S WHAT I'M GONNA DO.

01:53.447 --> 01:55.783
RYAN'S ORDERED YOU
TO GO AWAY BY YOURSELF.

01:55.816 --> 01:57.851
WHY WOULD HE DO THAT?

01:57.885 --> 02:00.254
WELL, YOU'D HAVE
TO ASK HIM THAT.

02:00.288 --> 02:02.623
* [ Continues ]

02:04.292 --> 02:07.661
I SHOULDN'T BE GONE
FOR MORE THAN
A COUPLE DAYS.

02:20.073 --> 02:23.677
- LOVE YOU.
- [ Truck Engine Starts ]

02:32.753 --> 02:36.224
[ Jonas On Radio ]
GENTLEMEN, LOOK ALIVE.
SALAZAR'S COMING OUT NOW.

02:41.495 --> 02:44.198
THAT MAY VERY WELL BE,
BUT ATTACKING SUPPLY
MAKES HEADLINES.

02:44.232 --> 02:47.067
IT'S THE MEN THAT--
THIS ADMINISTRATION
INTENDS...

02:47.100 --> 02:49.370
TO FIGHT THIS PLAGUE
ON ALL FRONTS.

02:49.403 --> 02:52.640
YES, BUT THIS
ADMINISTRATION HAS MADE--

02:52.673 --> 02:55.175
[ Audio Fades Out ]

03:03.617 --> 03:06.554
- GUN!
- DOWN! DOWN!

03:06.587 --> 03:08.556
DOWN! DOWN!

03:14.762 --> 03:16.464
[ Tires Squealing ]

03:20.200 --> 03:22.703
- [ Tires Squealing ]
- LET'S GET YOU INSIDE.

03:31.211 --> 03:33.381
[ Car Horn Honking ]

03:41.789 --> 03:44.325
- TAKE THE STRAIGHT--
- LINE. GOT IT.

03:51.565 --> 03:54.602
CLOSE THE GAP.
SÍ, SEÑOR.

04:01.108 --> 04:04.077
- I SEE YOU GOT YOUR LICENSE.
- LAST WEEK.

04:10.451 --> 04:12.486
I GOT HIM.
I GOT HIM.

04:26.867 --> 04:29.269
OUT!

04:29.303 --> 04:32.272
HANDS ON YOUR HEAD.

04:32.306 --> 04:35.609
[ Birds Twittering ]

04:43.717 --> 04:46.654
[ Gunshot ]

04:57.731 --> 05:01.301
LET'S SEE IF WE CAN'T FIND
WHERE YOUR FRIENDS WENT.

05:17.184 --> 05:20.287
YOU SHOULD HAVE CLEARED IT WITH
THE AGENCY. THAT'S MY FAMILY
THAT WAS INVOLVED.

05:20.320 --> 05:22.289
[ Man ]
ALL RIGHT.
HOLD ON, MR. SALAZAR.

05:22.322 --> 05:24.725
IS EVERYBODY WHOLE?
[ Williams ]
BOSS, WE GOT A PROBLEM.

05:24.758 --> 05:27.895
AFTER THE SHOOTING,
A CALL WENT OUT
TO SALAZAR'S FAMILY.

05:27.928 --> 05:30.631
HE'S GOT A WIFE, TWO BOYS.
THEY'RE ON THE WAY
TO SOME THEME PARK.

05:30.664 --> 05:32.866
THEY GOT THE CALL
TO TURN AROUND,
GO BACK TO THE HOTEL.

05:32.900 --> 05:34.802
ON THE WAY,
THEY WERE STOPPED.

05:34.835 --> 05:38.539
DRIVER WAS KILLED,
AND THE WIFE AND KIDS
WERE TAKEN.

05:38.572 --> 05:40.641
THIS WAS ONLY PART OF IT.

05:40.674 --> 05:43.210
- WHO WAS GUARDING THE FAMILY?
- PRIVATE OUTFIT. LOCAL.

05:43.243 --> 05:45.312
THEY WERE CLEARED
BY THE STATE DEPARTMENT.

05:45.345 --> 05:47.314
IF SOMEONE TOLD US,
WE COULD'VE PROTECTED THEM TOO.

05:47.347 --> 05:49.349
NO. WE HAD OUR JOB,
AND WE DID IT.

05:49.383 --> 05:52.219
NOW THAT THEY'VE
BEEN LOST, BOSS IS
GONNA WANT THEM FOUND.

06:04.865 --> 06:07.468
[ Woman On Radio, Indistinct ]

06:08.869 --> 06:10.938
WHAT'S THIS HAVE TO DO
WITH THE DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE?

06:10.971 --> 06:13.106
UNDETERMINED.

06:22.916 --> 06:25.753
- TWO VEHICLE JOB.
- ONE TO CUT THEM OFF,
SECOND TO ESCAPE.

06:25.786 --> 06:28.088
ALMOST LOOKS MILITARY.
SLOPPY, BUT MILITARY.

06:28.121 --> 06:32.392
THAT WOULD EXPLAIN
THE A.K.M.'s THE SHOOTERS
WE DEALT WITH WERE SPORTING.

06:32.426 --> 06:36.029
- WE CAN TRACE THE TRUCK.
- NO. THEY MEANT TO LEAVE IT.

06:36.063 --> 06:39.600
WHICH MEANS THEY MEANT
FOR US TO CHASE IT DOWN
SOME DEAD END. NO, THANKS.

06:44.838 --> 06:47.007
[ Woman On Radio, Indistinct ]

06:49.643 --> 06:52.245
SOMEONE KNEW THE FAMILY'S
RETURN ROUTE, KNEW TO
MEET THEM RIGHT HERE.

06:52.279 --> 06:55.015
INSIDE JOB.

07:00.120 --> 07:02.422
[ Call And Response ]
* FIRED UP
FIRED UP *

07:02.456 --> 07:04.792
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP *

07:04.825 --> 07:07.260
* HERE WE GO
ON THE ROAD *

07:07.294 --> 07:09.396
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP *

07:09.429 --> 07:11.499
* FIRED UP
FIRED UP *

07:11.532 --> 07:14.535
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP *

07:23.877 --> 07:26.847
PROBLEM?
OUR PRISONER.

07:26.880 --> 07:29.016
WE'RE HAVING A BIT
OF A CUSTODY DISPUTE.

07:29.049 --> 07:30.851
YOU TELL HER ANYTHING?
JUST THAT HE'S OURS.

07:30.884 --> 07:33.320
GOOD.
KEEP IT THAT WAY.

07:33.353 --> 07:36.857
BOSSES WANT THE LOCALS AND PRESS
KEPT IN THE DARK ABOUT THE
KIDNAPPING UNTIL WE FIND THEM.

07:36.890 --> 07:39.527
WE'LL BE TAKING HIM NOW.

07:39.560 --> 07:43.130
NO WAY IN HELL.
NOT WITHOUT ME TALKING
TO YOUR BOSS FIRST.

07:43.163 --> 07:45.298
GIVE ME YOUR PHONE.

07:51.805 --> 07:53.807
[ Line Ringing ]

07:53.841 --> 07:55.809
[ Operator ]
WHITE HOUSE SWITCHBOARD.

07:55.843 --> 07:58.345
ASK FOR THE PRESIDENT.
HOW MAY I
DIRECT YOUR CALL?

08:00.814 --> 08:03.416
[ Bird Twittering ]

08:26.406 --> 08:30.544
[ Grunting, Shouting ]

08:32.613 --> 08:35.215
[ Panting ]

08:44.758 --> 08:48.395
CALL THE OFFICE.
I WANT AN UPDATE
FROM OUR END RIGHT NOW.

08:48.428 --> 08:50.430
STATE DEPARTMENT'S
GOT CONFIRMATION...

08:50.463 --> 08:54.768
THAT THE TWO SHOOTERS
AND OUR DRIVER ARE IN
THE MEXICAN ARMY.

08:54.802 --> 08:57.705
- CURRENTLY ON FURLOUGHS.
- PRESUMABLY ON THE PAYROLL
OF THE CARTELS.

08:57.738 --> 08:59.873
THIS IS TO INTIMIDATE
SALAZAR AND HIS GOVERNMENT...

08:59.907 --> 09:01.942
FROM MAKING THOSE REFORMS
THEY PROMISED.

09:01.975 --> 09:04.745
WE DO NOT--
ANIMALES.

09:08.415 --> 09:10.851
THE KIDNAPPERS HAVE
CONTACTED MY OFFICE.

09:10.884 --> 09:15.288
THEY ARE DEMANDING THE RELEASE
OF 120 CARTEL PRISONERS
WITHIN THE NEXT HOUR,

09:15.322 --> 09:18.225
AS WELL AS AN END
TO ANY NEW NEGOTIATIONS
WITH THE AMERICANS.

09:18.258 --> 09:20.393
- SO THEY'RE JUST
MAKING A POINT---
- OR?

09:20.427 --> 09:23.931
OR TONIGHT THEY WILL
KILL CAMILLE...

09:23.964 --> 09:26.099
AND MY TWO BOYS.

09:34.407 --> 09:37.144
[ Door Opens ]
I DEMAND A LAWYER,
AS IS MY RIGHT.

09:37.177 --> 09:41.915
LAWYERS ARE FOR
ACCUSED CRIMINALS.

09:41.949 --> 09:44.918
YOU, ON THE OTHER HAND,
ARE A SOLDIER
IN THE MEXICAN ARMY,

09:44.952 --> 09:47.054
WHO MADE THE GRAVE
MISCALCULATION...

09:47.087 --> 09:49.823
OF INVADING THE UNITED STATES
WITH WOEFULLY INADEQUATE FORCES.

09:49.857 --> 09:53.426
NO. HABEAS CORPUS WENT OUT
THE WINDOW FOR YOU, FRIEND.

09:56.196 --> 09:58.465
YOU ARE A PRISONER OF WAR.

10:06.039 --> 10:08.909
[ Woman ]
V & M REALTORS.
HOLD, PLEASE.

10:08.942 --> 10:11.611
HELLO.
THANK YOU.

10:13.180 --> 10:16.917
ARE YOU LOOKING
FOR A BUYER'S AGENT
OR A SELLER'S AGENT?

10:16.950 --> 10:19.787
YOU GAVE THE ARMORY
PROPERTY TO KYLE.
YOU GAVE HIM THE ARMORY LISTING.

10:19.820 --> 10:21.855
I TRIED TO CALL YOU.
I BROUGHT THEM IN.

10:21.889 --> 10:24.091
WE ALL BROUGHT THEM IN.
IT WAS A TEAM EFFORT.

10:24.124 --> 10:26.626
AND NOW KYLE
HAS THE LISTINGS.
I LEFT YOU MESSAGES.

10:26.660 --> 10:29.362
- I CALLED YOU BACK.
- AFTER WE CLOSED.

10:29.396 --> 10:32.833
THE ARMORY PEOPLE
GOT COLD FEET.
THEY NEEDED A HUG.

10:32.866 --> 10:35.669
I CALLED YOU FIRST. NO ANSWER.
SO I SENT KYLE DOWN THERE.

10:35.703 --> 10:37.938
BUT I CALLED YOU FIRST.

10:37.971 --> 10:41.341
- I WAS WITH A NEIGHBOR OF MINE.
- WELL, IF YOUR SOCIAL LIFE
GOT IN THE WAY--

10:41.374 --> 10:43.543
HER HUSBAND WAS
JUST KILLED IN COMBAT.

10:44.678 --> 10:47.948
- WELL, THAT'S--
- I HAD RESPONSIBILITIES.

10:47.981 --> 10:50.217
I SENT KYLE
TO SETTLE THEM DOWN.
WHICH HE DID.

10:50.250 --> 10:53.486
THEY CALLED BACK AND SAID
THEY WANTED TO WORK WITH HIM.

10:53.520 --> 10:55.355
THESE THINGS HAPPEN WHEN
YOU'VE GOT ONE FOOT IN--

10:55.388 --> 10:58.158
NO. DO NOT.
I'M DEDICATED.

10:58.191 --> 11:00.794
WHEN YOU'RE HERE.
WHICH, THREE YEARS LATER,
IS STILL PART-TIME.

11:00.828 --> 11:02.830
THE OTHERS--

11:08.601 --> 11:10.871
THE LIST PRICE
IS TOO LOW.

11:10.904 --> 11:14.341
AT THE ARMORY.
IT'S PRICED TOO LOW.
THE CLIENT'S SATISFIED.

11:14.374 --> 11:18.178
IT'S WORTH 15,
20% MORE THAN THAT.

11:19.346 --> 11:22.049
- I'LL TELL KYLE.
- YOU DO THAT.

11:31.624 --> 11:34.862
[ Breathing Heavily ]

11:38.131 --> 11:40.868
[ Grunts ]

11:56.483 --> 11:58.485
MAN,
I'M NO THREAT TO YOU.

12:01.488 --> 12:04.892
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU'RE GROWIN' OR BREWIN'
UP HERE, AND I DON'T CARE.

12:04.925 --> 12:08.862
I'M HURT,
AND I NEED HELP.

12:08.896 --> 12:11.031
I THINK
MY SHOULDER'S BUSTED.

12:11.064 --> 12:14.935
BUSTED SHOULDER, HUH?
HOW'D YOU DO THAT?

12:14.968 --> 12:17.237
I FELL.

12:17.270 --> 12:19.639
DANGEROUS PLACE
TO BE FALLIN'.

12:19.672 --> 12:21.942
[ Sighs ]
FRIEND, I'M HURT.

12:21.975 --> 12:24.611
IF YOU CAN'T DO ANYTHING
FOR ME, JUST POINT ME
IN THE RIGHT DIRECTION.

12:24.644 --> 12:26.746
I'LL GET OUT OF YOUR A.O.

12:26.780 --> 12:29.049
A.O.?

12:29.082 --> 12:32.552
THIS ISN'T ANYBODY'S
AREA OF OPERATION.

12:32.585 --> 12:35.956
YOU JUST HAVE TO BE
CAREFUL WHO'S WANDERING
AROUND HERE THESE DAYS.

12:38.625 --> 12:40.794
PARATROOPER, HUH?

12:40.828 --> 12:44.064
IN MY YOUTH.
WELL, HELL, SON.
WHY DIDN'T YOU SAY SO?

12:44.097 --> 12:46.166
THAT COUNTS
FOR A LOT OF SINS.

12:46.199 --> 12:50.770
COME ON.
I'LL GET YOU
SQUARED AWAY.

13:10.723 --> 13:13.426
[ Woman ]
ORDER WHATEVER YOU WANT.
IT'S ON ME.

13:13.460 --> 13:15.695
NO.
OH, DON'T BE
RIDICULOUS.

13:15.728 --> 13:17.797
WE'LL SPLIT IT.
OF COURSE.
WE'LL SPLIT IT.

13:17.831 --> 13:20.633
NO. NO, NO, NO, NO.
I INVITED YOU.
I'M PAYING.

13:20.667 --> 13:24.471
IT'S A TREAT TO BE BACK
WITH OLD FRIENDS, AND HAVE
A CHANCE TO MAKE NEW ONES.

13:24.504 --> 13:26.874
- SO LUNCH IS ON ME.
- LET'S SEE THIS NEW HOUSE
WE'VE BEEN HEARING ABOUT.

13:26.907 --> 13:29.843
WELL, WE'RE HALF AN HOUR
NORTH OF SAN DIEGO,

13:29.877 --> 13:31.845
AND ONLY A COUPLE
OF BLOCKS FROM THE OCEAN.

13:31.879 --> 13:34.614
- CYNTHIA.
- OH, IT'S LOVELY.

13:34.647 --> 13:36.850
- HOW--
- DO WE AFFORD IT?
[ Chuckles ]

13:36.884 --> 13:39.452
ANDREW'S BEEN DOING
CONTRACT WORK.
KUWAIT, BOLIVIA.

13:39.486 --> 13:43.957
HE WAS BORING HIMSELF TO TEARS,
FLOPPING AROUND THE BASEMENT
DOING WOODWORK.

13:43.991 --> 13:47.327
SO I HAD TO KICK
HIS BUTT BACK OUT
INTO THE REAL WORLD.

13:47.360 --> 13:50.197
MERCENARY WORK?
DRIVING, PROTECTION.

13:50.230 --> 13:52.866
SAME THINGS HE WAS
DOING IN THE UNIT,
ONLY NOT AS DANGEROUS.

13:52.900 --> 13:55.368
AND THE PAY--
[ Scoffs ]

13:55.402 --> 13:58.205
I MEAN, KIM, YOU'RE THE NEWBIE.
HOW MUCH THEY STARTING
YOUR HUSBAND OUT AT?

13:58.238 --> 14:00.807
$38,600 A YEAR.

14:00.840 --> 14:03.043
PLUS COMBAT PAY.

14:03.076 --> 14:05.879
AND HOW MUCH IS
BETSY'S TUITION COSTING
YOU AND JONAS THIS YEAR?

14:05.913 --> 14:08.681
TWENTY?
A LITTLE BIT MORE.

14:08.715 --> 14:12.385
SOMEONE WITH UNIT EXPERIENCE
MAKES MID SIX FIGURES
IN THE PRIVATE SECTOR.

14:12.419 --> 14:14.321
[ Woman Whistles ]
[ Molly ]
WELL.

14:14.354 --> 14:16.890
GOOD FOR YOU AND ANDREW.
THAT'S WHY WE'RE STARTING
OUR OWN COMPANY.

14:16.924 --> 14:19.759
WE'VE GOT CONTRACTS
IN KUWAIT AND SAUDI ARABIA.

14:19.792 --> 14:23.263
AND WE'RE LOOKING FOR MEN
TO FILL THEM. UNIT MEN.

14:23.296 --> 14:26.499
PAYS $300,000 A YEAR
TO START, AND TWO MONTHS
VACATION TIME.

14:26.533 --> 14:29.236
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

14:29.269 --> 14:31.871
THEY COULD ALL OPT OUT
OF THE UNIT TOMORROW
IF THEY WANT--

14:31.905 --> 14:34.541
WELL, EXCEPT FOR BOB--
AND COME WORK WITH US.

14:34.574 --> 14:37.911
MACK WOULDN'T KNOW WHAT TO DO
WITH A HUNDRED-DOLLAR BILL IF
YOU GAVE HIM A SLIDE SHOW ON IT.

14:37.945 --> 14:40.680
[ Laughter ]
BUT WE WOULD,
WOULDN'T WE?

14:40.713 --> 14:43.850
PAY THE GAS BILL,
COLLEGE TUITION.

14:43.883 --> 14:47.754
THINK ABOUT THE FUTURE.
THAT'S WHY I'M TALKING
TO YOU, NOT THEM.

14:47.787 --> 14:51.358
WHAT ABOUT THE UNIT,
IF THEY ALL RAN OFF
TO DO CONTRACT WORK?

14:51.391 --> 14:54.561
ANDREW'S FIGHTING
THE SAME WAR AS JONAS
AND THE REST OF THEM.

14:54.594 --> 14:57.030
HE'S JUST GETTING PAID
COMMENSURATE TO HIS ABILITIES.

14:57.064 --> 15:01.368
AND HE'S GETTING TREATED
WITH RESPECT, AND SO AM I.

15:01.401 --> 15:04.871
I MEAN, DO YOU HAVE ANY CLUE
WHERE MACK IS TODAY?
WHERE HE MIGHT BE NEXT WEEK?

15:04.904 --> 15:07.540
- OF COURSE NOT.
- WOULDN'T YOU LIKE TO KNOW?

15:07.574 --> 15:10.543
WE ALL WOULD.
BUT YOU DON'T.

15:10.577 --> 15:13.313
AND THAT'S NO WAY
TO RUN A MARRIAGE.

15:13.346 --> 15:15.983
WHAT KIND OF WORK WOULD
THEY BE DOING EXACTLY?

15:16.016 --> 15:18.818
WELL, IT RUNS THE GAMUT.
AND THERE'S ALWAYS
A JOB WAITING.

15:24.691 --> 15:26.926
NEWS?

15:26.960 --> 15:30.663
WE WERE DOWN AT THE SECURITY
FIRM THAT WAS RUNNING PROTECTION
ON SALAZAR'S FAMILY.

15:30.697 --> 15:33.266
TURNED US ON
TO THE DRIVER'S FIANCÉE.
UNCOOPERATIVE AT FIRST.

15:33.300 --> 15:35.468
THE DRIVER WAS IN ON IT.
GAVE UP THE ROUTE.

15:35.502 --> 15:38.071
OFFERED TO PLAY ALONG
AS THE TERRIFIED VICTIM.

15:38.105 --> 15:39.973
HE WAS SUPPOSED TO GET
25 GRAND FOR HIS TROUBLES.

15:40.007 --> 15:42.409
GOT A COUPLE OF BULLETS INSTEAD.
LIFE'S FUNNY THAT WAY.

15:42.442 --> 15:45.245
THE GIRL KNOW ANYTHING ELSE?
JUST THAT THE KIDNAP TEAM
WAS FIVE STRONG.

15:45.278 --> 15:48.015
NO I.D., NO LOCATION.
MEANS HE'S OUR ONLY LINK.

15:48.048 --> 15:51.184
YES, HE IS.

15:51.218 --> 15:54.587
THE PRESIDENT BELIEVES
THIS CAN BEST BE HANDLED BY
COLONEL RYAN'S ORGANIZATION.

15:54.621 --> 15:58.325
AND FROM THE STANDPOINT--
THEIR JOB WAS PROTECTION.
THIS IS NOW A KIDNAPPING.

15:58.358 --> 16:01.028
MY MEN HAVE FEET ON THE GROUND.
THEY'RE ALREADY MAKING PROGRESS.

16:01.061 --> 16:03.296
AND THEY CAN PASS ON WHAT
THEY'VE LEARNED TO THE BUREAU.

16:03.330 --> 16:05.832
SO YOU CAN SIT ON
YOUR HANDS AGAIN
LIKE THAT INCIDENT IN IDAHO.

16:05.865 --> 16:08.535
- I WAS NOT COMPLICITOUS
IN THE DEATHS OF--
- GENTLEMEN. GENTLEMEN!

16:08.568 --> 16:11.838
THE PRESIDENT FEELS
AS LONG AS THE KIDNAPPINGS
HAVEN'T HIT THE PRESS,

16:11.871 --> 16:13.940
THE COLONEL'S COVERT UNIT
REPRESENTS THE BEST CHANCE...

16:13.973 --> 16:16.176
OF GETTING THE SALAZAR
FAMILY BACK ALIVE.

16:16.209 --> 16:18.811
SHOULD THE KIDNAPPINGS
BECOME PUBLIC,
THE PRESIDENT WILL...

16:18.845 --> 16:21.681
REEVALUATE OUR OPTIONS
AT THAT TIME.

16:21.714 --> 16:24.651
SUSAN, JUSTICE IS SATISFIED
THAT THE PRESIDENT'S DECISION
IS THE CORRECT ONE.

16:24.684 --> 16:27.287
AND WE WILL SUPPORT
THE DEPARTMENT OF DEFENSE
IN THIS MATTER...

16:27.320 --> 16:29.222
TO THE MAXIMUM
OF OUR CAPABILITIES.

16:29.256 --> 16:31.491
REST ASSURED, DOUG,
D.O.D. WILL COORDINATE WITH...

16:31.524 --> 16:33.726
AND COOPERATE FULLY WITH
THE DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE.

16:33.760 --> 16:35.928
LET'S SEE IF WE CAN RESOLVE IT
WITH NO MORE DAMAGE BEING DONE.

16:38.331 --> 16:40.500
GENTLEMEN.

16:44.003 --> 16:47.006
[ Door Closes ]
WE WON ONE
FOR OUR SIDE, TOM.

16:47.040 --> 16:50.077
I HOPE TO THINK
WE'RE ON THE SAME
SIDE, GENERAL.

16:50.110 --> 16:53.080
GIVE AND TAKE IS ESSENTIAL
TO THE BELTWAY PROCESS.

16:53.113 --> 16:55.715
IT'S HOW PRECEDENCE
IS ESTABLISHED.
IT'S HOW POWER IS WIELDED.

16:55.748 --> 16:58.385
SIR, I BOW TO
YOUR GREATER EXPERIENCE.

16:58.418 --> 17:00.987
THE ARMY HAS GREAT THINGS
IN STORE FOR YOU.

17:01.020 --> 17:04.023
COMBAT IN WASHINGTON
IS WHERE THE ARMY FIGHTS
ITS GREATEST BATTLES.

17:05.625 --> 17:07.527
YOU HAVE ANY AMBITIONS
IN D.C., TOM?

17:07.560 --> 17:09.696
NO, SIR.

17:09.729 --> 17:14.033
WELL, D.C. MAY STILL
HAVE AMBITIONS FOR YOU.

17:14.067 --> 17:16.736
I'LL SEE YOU AT THE PENTAGON
IN THE MORNING.

17:19.939 --> 17:22.209
[ Cell Phone Clicks, Beeps ]

17:23.310 --> 17:26.179
[ Cell Phone Beeps ]

17:26.213 --> 17:29.616
GO FOR BLANE.
ALL RIGHT, JONAS.
YOU GOT THE JOB.

17:29.649 --> 17:31.918
THERE'S NO COURT-MARTIAL
IN MY FUTURE?

17:31.951 --> 17:33.620
AS LONG AS THIS THING
STAYS SECRET, IT'S YOURS,

17:33.653 --> 17:36.089
WHICH MEANS WE CAN COUNT ON
THE BUREAU LEAKING SOMETHING
ANY MINUTE.

17:36.123 --> 17:38.225
SO PUT A FLAME UNDER IT.
ROGER THAT.

17:38.258 --> 17:40.227
WHERE DO WE STAND?

17:40.260 --> 17:43.029
WE'RE SETTING UP
FOR VOICE STRESS ANALYSIS.
GOOD.

17:43.062 --> 17:45.064
KEEP CHECKING IN.
[ Cell Phone Clicks ]

17:47.767 --> 17:49.869
[ Jonas On Radio ]
TEST, TEST, TEST.
I COPY.

17:49.902 --> 17:53.072
- VOICE STRESS ANALYSIS READY.
- AND BEGIN.

17:55.642 --> 17:57.910
YOU ARE A U.S. PRISONER OF WAR,

17:57.944 --> 18:01.148
AND YOU WILL BE TREATED
ACCORDING TO THE ARTICLES
OF THE GENEVA CONVENTION.

18:01.181 --> 18:03.716
- DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME?
- SÍ.

18:03.750 --> 18:05.618
WELL, THAT'S SPANISH
FOR YES. CORRECT?

18:05.652 --> 18:08.655
YES.
I'M GONNA ASK YOU SOME
QUESTIONS NOW, MIGUEL.

18:08.688 --> 18:11.791
AND YOU'RE GONNA TELL ME
THE ABSOLUTE TRUTH.
YOU KNOW WHY THAT IS?

18:11.824 --> 18:13.993
BECAUSE YOU ARE NOT
A TRUE BELIEVER.

18:14.026 --> 18:16.095
MONEY HAS BEEN YOUR
MAIN MOTIVATION TODAY.

18:16.129 --> 18:19.166
WHICH MEANS YOUR ALLEGIANCES
ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE.

18:19.199 --> 18:21.468
I'M HERE TO SHOW YOU
ANOTHER PATH.

18:21.501 --> 18:23.503
[ Jonas ]
WHAT IS YOUR FULL NAME?

18:23.536 --> 18:26.306
MIGUEL HORATIO DOMINGUEZ.

18:26.339 --> 18:29.476
HOW OLD ARE YOU?
26.

18:29.509 --> 18:31.978
- AND WHERE ARE YOU FROM?
- MÉXICO.

18:32.011 --> 18:34.414
YOU'RE A SOLDIER
IN THE MEXICAN ARMY?

18:34.447 --> 18:36.683
YES.

18:36.716 --> 18:38.785
[ Monitor Beeps ]
BASELINE ESTABLISHED.

18:38.818 --> 18:41.321
PROCEED WITH
YOUR INTERROGATION.

18:41.354 --> 18:43.990
WHO IS MONGOOSE?

18:44.023 --> 18:46.993
- I DON'T KNOW.
- LIE.

18:47.026 --> 18:50.830
IS THAT RIGHT?
LET'S TRY THAT ONE AGAIN.

18:50.863 --> 18:52.865
WHO IS THE MAN
CODE-NAMED MONGOOSE?

18:54.367 --> 18:56.669
IF MY QUESTIONS
DON'T PRODUCE THE TRUTH,

18:56.703 --> 18:59.506
OTHER ACCOMMODATIONS,
LESS PLEASANT--

18:59.539 --> 19:01.641
YOU UNDERSTAND ME--
CAN BE ARRANGED.

19:01.674 --> 19:05.011
WHO IS MONGOOSE?

19:05.044 --> 19:08.715
I HEARD OTHERS TALK OF HIM,
BUT I DON'T KNOW WHO HE IS.

19:08.748 --> 19:10.883
[ Monitor Beeps ]
TRUE.

19:10.917 --> 19:13.386
BUT HE IS THE MAN
IN CHARGE OF THIS MISSION...

19:13.420 --> 19:16.656
TO KILL SENOR SALAZAR
AND KIDNAP HIS FAMILY?

19:16.689 --> 19:19.326
IT IS WHAT I HEARD.
[ Operator ]
TRUE.

19:19.359 --> 19:23.563
WHERE ARE YOUR FRIENDS
HOLDING HIS WIFE
AND TWO YOUNG SONS?

19:23.596 --> 19:26.165
I DON'T KNOW.
TRUE.

19:27.700 --> 19:29.902
WHERE CAN I FIND
THE OTHERS INVOLVED?

19:31.103 --> 19:33.039
- I DON'T KNOW.
- LIE.

19:35.908 --> 19:38.144
I DON'T MEAN
TO DOUBT YOUR WORD,

19:38.177 --> 19:40.880
BUT THAT'S THE SECOND TIME
YOU'VE LIED TO ME.

19:40.913 --> 19:42.982
A THIRD TIME AND THINGS
WILL BECOME DIFFICULT.

19:43.015 --> 19:45.151
DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME?

19:45.184 --> 19:48.721
- YES.
- TRUE.

19:48.755 --> 19:51.023
I HOPE YOU
BY GOD DO, SON.

19:51.057 --> 19:53.092
NOW WHERE CAN I FIND
THE OTHERS?

19:55.628 --> 19:59.866
WE WERE SUPPOSED TO MEET
AT 2100 HOURS TONIGHT...

19:59.899 --> 20:02.235
TO LEAVE TO MEXICO TOGETHER.

20:02.269 --> 20:05.572
- TRUE.
- DO THEY INTEND TO KILL
THE SALAZAR FAMILY...

20:05.605 --> 20:09.376
BEFORE THEY MEET YOU
AT 2100?

20:09.409 --> 20:12.011
YES. WHEN THEY RECEIVE
THE ORDER FROM MONGOOSE.

20:12.044 --> 20:13.980
[ Beeps ]
TRUE.

20:23.222 --> 20:26.559
THE LAST THING THIS PLACE
NEEDS IS FOR YOU TO THROW
A GRENADE INTO THE BARRACKS,

20:26.593 --> 20:28.361
DECIMATING THE RANKS.

20:28.395 --> 20:30.797
IF IT'S NOT ME, MOLLY,
IT'LL BE SOMEONE ELSE,
AND SOON.

20:30.830 --> 20:33.766
THESE MEN ARE WANTED.
THEY ARE WANTED BAD.

20:33.800 --> 20:37.537
AND LOOK,
WE DON'T JUST WANT JONAS.
WE'D LIKE YOU TOO.

20:37.570 --> 20:43.042
- FOR WHAT?
- PLANNING, LOGISTICS,
PAYROLL, RECRUITMENT.

20:43.075 --> 20:45.912
WE NEED OPERATORS,
AND I NEED HELP.

20:45.945 --> 20:48.047
I'LL PAY YOU $5,000
FOR ANY UNIT MEMBERS
THAT COME OVER.

20:48.080 --> 20:50.550
5,000 A HEAD?
THAT'S RIGHT.

20:50.583 --> 20:53.986
LIKE CATTLE.
THAT AIN'T GONNA MAKE
THE MONEY GO AWAY, HON.

20:54.020 --> 20:56.623
AND WHAT ABOUT THE WIVES--
YOUR WIVES?

20:56.656 --> 20:59.959
WHAT DO THEY DO
WITHOUT THIS COMMUNITY,
WITHOUT THE REST OF US?

20:59.992 --> 21:03.963
BELIEVE IT OR NOT, MOLLY,
THERE IS ACTUALLY LIFE
OUT OF THE ARMY.

21:07.334 --> 21:09.569
HOW ARE YOU AND JONAS
DOING LATELY?

21:09.602 --> 21:11.738
GREAT.
REALLY?

21:11.771 --> 21:13.640
WHAT DID I JUST SAY?

21:15.007 --> 21:17.444
AND WHAT ABOUT
YOU AND ANDREW?

21:17.477 --> 21:19.579
NEVER BEEN BETTER.
IT'S LIKE THE HONEYMOON
WE NEVER HAD.

21:19.612 --> 21:22.482
IS THAT RIGHT?
YES, IT IS.

21:22.515 --> 21:25.652
AND WHY IS THAT?
MONEY?

21:25.685 --> 21:27.987
IS THAT WHY
YOU'RE TELLING ME?

21:28.020 --> 21:30.357
IT'S BECAUSE
WE'RE WORKING TOGETHER.

21:30.390 --> 21:34.827
FOR THE FIRST TIME IN 20 YEARS,
WE ARE SHARING THE SAME LIFE.

21:34.861 --> 21:37.997
DOES THAT SOUND
LIKE SOMETHING?

21:38.030 --> 21:40.166
WE NEED TO GET A LID ON THIS
BEFORE PEOPLE GET IDEAS.

21:40.199 --> 21:42.935
- WHAT WE NEED TO DO
IS TALK THIS THROUGH.
- TALK WHAT--

21:42.969 --> 21:47.707
I WANT THE WIVES HERE TONIGHT.
I DON'T LIKE THE QUESTIONS
THAT SAMANTHA WAS ASKING.

21:47.740 --> 21:51.511
TIFFY, I--
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?
MY TRIP.

21:51.544 --> 21:53.813
I NEED YOU HERE TONIGHT.

21:53.846 --> 21:56.182
I'VE GOT A TICKET.
THE KIDS ARE TAKEN CARE OF.

21:56.215 --> 21:59.051
BUT MACK--
DOES THAT MEAN
I CAN'T GO?

21:59.085 --> 22:01.287
I DESERVE TO GO, RIGHT?

22:01.320 --> 22:04.190
I NEED YOU HERE
TO HELP ME TALK
THIS THROUGH.

22:04.223 --> 22:06.292
YOU DON'T NEED ME.
YOU'LL BE FINE.

22:06.325 --> 22:09.529
I'LL BE FINE?
I KNOW I'LL BE FINE.

22:09.562 --> 22:12.231
WHAT I NEED IS SOLIDARITY.

22:12.264 --> 22:15.868
BUT ME-- WHAT I NEED
THIS PARTICULAR MOMENT--

22:15.902 --> 22:18.270
I NEED TO
CATCH A PLANE.

22:20.740 --> 22:23.410
[ Car Door Closes ]

22:23.443 --> 22:25.545
[ Man Speaking Spanish ]
WE KNOW WHERE
THEY WILL BE.

22:25.578 --> 22:28.047
BUT ONLY AFTER
THEY KILL MY FAMILY.
WE STILL HAVE TIME.

22:28.080 --> 22:30.483
SHE ASKED ME
NOT TO TAKE THIS JOB.

22:30.517 --> 22:32.685
CAMILLE, MY WIFE,
SHE BEGGED ME
NOT TO TAKE IT.

22:32.719 --> 22:36.656
TOO DANGEROUS.
I CONVINCED HER
THINGS COULD CHANGE.

22:36.689 --> 22:38.825
I WILL DO EVERYTHING
I CAN TO HELP YOU.

22:38.858 --> 22:41.894
[ Door Opens ]
JONAS.

22:41.928 --> 22:44.864
A REPORTER DOWNSTAIRS.
WELL, THAT DIDN'T TAKE LONG.

22:44.897 --> 22:48.034
THREATENING TO BREAK
THE KIDNAPPING ANGLE
ON THE 6:00 NEWS.

22:48.067 --> 22:50.102
SHE CAN'T DO THAT.
SHE'S GOT THE STORY.

22:50.136 --> 22:52.605
IT IS A FREE PRESS.
SAYS WHO?

22:53.940 --> 22:56.443
BRING HER UP HERE.
NOW.

22:56.476 --> 22:58.377
UH-HUH.

23:34.180 --> 23:36.315
YOU STAY HERE.

23:54.266 --> 23:56.669
JACK TELLS ME
YOU'RE INJURED.

23:56.703 --> 23:59.639
I DON'T KNOW IF
IT'S BROKE OR OUT OF JOINT,
BUT IT HURTS LIKE HELL.

23:59.672 --> 24:02.008
WELL, YOU'VE DONE A GOOD JOB
OF IMMOBILIZING IT.

24:02.041 --> 24:04.176
LET'S TAKE A CLOSER LOOK.

24:05.945 --> 24:09.181
HERE, SERGEANT.
PUT THIS AWAY FOR OUR FRIEND
UNTIL HE'S READY TO LEAVE.

24:14.687 --> 24:16.556
PLEASE.

24:22.962 --> 24:26.098
JACK, YOU SEE,
IS LIKE THE SCARECROW.

24:26.132 --> 24:30.036
HIS FUNCTION IS TO
FRIGHTEN AWAY THE CURIOUS
AND THE CASUALLY INTRUSIVE.

24:30.069 --> 24:33.172
AND LIKE THE SCARECROW,

24:33.205 --> 24:36.342
HE IS HARMLESS
IN AND OF HIMSELF.

24:36.375 --> 24:39.111
AND AS FOR YOUR ARM,
YOUNG MAN,

24:39.145 --> 24:42.281
IT IS DISLOCATED
AND NOT BROKEN.

24:42.314 --> 24:45.017
AND IF YOU FEEL YOU CAN
BEAR THE DISCOMFORT,

24:45.051 --> 24:46.786
I'LL PUT IT BACK
IN PLACE FOR YOU.

24:46.819 --> 24:49.055
[ Mack Gasps ]
YES?

24:51.190 --> 24:55.227
KEEP YOUR ELBOW
AT YOUR SIDE.
MAKE A FIST.

24:55.261 --> 24:57.496
[ Grunts, Shouts ]
[ Bones Cracking ]

24:57.530 --> 24:59.966
STOP! STOP!
NO GOOD?

24:59.999 --> 25:03.169
THAT'S WORSE.
MY APOLOGIES.

25:03.202 --> 25:05.237
IN THE MORNING,
I'LL HAVE JACK...

25:05.271 --> 25:07.540
LEAD YOU DOWN THE MOUNTAIN
TO THE NEAREST DOCTOR.

25:07.574 --> 25:09.842
UNTIL THEN,

25:09.876 --> 25:11.778
GET OUR FRIEND
SOMETHING TO DRINK.

25:16.683 --> 25:18.585
[ Glasses Clink ]

25:18.618 --> 25:20.820
HERE SHE IS.
NO CAMERAS.

25:20.853 --> 25:23.522
JUST YOU.
HEY.

25:26.125 --> 25:30.529
WHAT DO YOU KNOW?
WHAT DO YOU INTEND
TO REPORT?

25:30.563 --> 25:33.365
I KNOW THERE WAS AN ATTEMPT
ON MR. SALAZAR'S LIFE TODAY.

25:33.399 --> 25:35.702
TWO MEN WERE KILLED.
A THIRD IS PRESUMABLY
IN CUSTODY.

25:35.735 --> 25:38.237
AND NOW I HEAR
AN APPARENT CARJACKING IS,
IN REALITY,

25:38.270 --> 25:41.073
A KIDNAPPING OF
MR. SALAZAR'S FAMILY.

25:41.107 --> 25:44.443
ALL TRUE, AND YOU CAN'T
BROADCAST ANY OF IT.
WHY NOT?

25:44.476 --> 25:47.614
BECAUSE ONCE NEWS OF
THE KIDNAPPING IS MADE PUBLIC,

25:47.647 --> 25:50.617
THE FAMILY WILL BE
MORE VALUABLE TO THEM DEAD.

25:50.650 --> 25:54.453
ALSO, IF THEY LEARN THAT
ONE OF THEIR COMPATRIOTS
IS ALIVE AND TALKING WITH US,

25:54.486 --> 25:57.456
THEY WON'T MAKE IT
TO THEIR APPOINTED RENDEZVOUS
WHERE WE WILL BE WAITING.

25:57.489 --> 26:00.059
IF I FOUND THIS STORY,
SOMEONE ELSE WILL TOO.

26:00.092 --> 26:02.428
I'M NOT LETTING
ANOTHER STATION BEAT ME.

26:02.461 --> 26:04.731
I WANT YOU TO HOLD OFF--
TWO HOURS.

26:04.764 --> 26:07.399
ONLY IF YOU LET ME
FILM THEIR CAPTURE.
UNACCEPTABLE.

26:07.433 --> 26:09.769
BUT WHAT I DO NEED YOU
TO DO RIGHT NOW IS TO REPORT...

26:09.802 --> 26:11.871
THAT ALL THREE SHOOTERS
WERE KILLED THIS MORNING.

26:11.904 --> 26:13.973
I AM NOT IN THE BUSINESS
OF LYING TO MY VIEWERS.

26:14.006 --> 26:16.275
OH. IS THAT SO?

26:16.308 --> 26:18.745
I HAVE A JOB TO DO.

26:18.778 --> 26:22.148
I WANT YOU TO POSTPONE IT.
WHY SHOULD I?

26:23.850 --> 26:26.018
TAKE THIS CARD.

26:28.755 --> 26:31.123
HOLD ONTO IT.

26:31.157 --> 26:35.127
WHAT IS THAT?
NO MATTER HOW BLESSED
OUR LIVES,

26:35.161 --> 26:37.630
HOW CHARMED OUR EXISTENCE,

26:37.664 --> 26:41.634
THINGS STILL INEVITABLY,
IRREVOCABLY, GO WRONG.

26:41.668 --> 26:45.104
YOUR MOTHER'S SWINDLED
OUT OF HER SAVINGS.

26:45.137 --> 26:47.807
YOUR ESTRANGED HUSBAND
RUNS OFF WITH YOUR KIDS.

26:47.840 --> 26:50.409
YOUR BEST FRIEND
GOES ON VACATION
IN A FOREIGN LAND...

26:50.442 --> 26:52.745
AND DISAPPEARS.

26:52.779 --> 26:56.448
EVENTUALLY BAD THINGS
FIND US ALL.

26:56.482 --> 27:00.252
YOU EVER HEAR OF
THE "GET OUT OF JAIL FREE" CARD?

27:00.286 --> 27:03.589
THIS IS
A "GET OUT OF HELL" CARD.

27:03.622 --> 27:07.860
AT SOME POINT IN YOUR LIFE,
GOD FORBID YOU HAVE
NOWHERE ELSE TO TURN,

27:07.894 --> 27:10.162
CALL THAT NUMBER.

27:12.999 --> 27:16.035
THAT IS WHY YOU ARE GOING
TO POSTPONE YOUR JOB.

27:22.742 --> 27:24.877
TWO HOURS.

27:28.180 --> 27:31.350
* [ Piano ]

27:34.754 --> 27:38.557
PRETTY GOOD TRIP
TO D.C., EH?

27:38.590 --> 27:41.127
WON ONE FOR THE HOME TEAM.

27:41.160 --> 27:43.629
LAST TIME I CHECKED,
THE AMERICAN PEOPLE PAY
BOTH OUR SALARIES.

27:43.662 --> 27:46.532
WHY DON'T WE JUST TRY
TO GIVE THEM
THEIR MONEY'S WORTH.

27:46.565 --> 27:49.969
WELL, THAT'S VERY POETIC.
IS IT?

27:50.002 --> 27:53.840
THAT COMMENT YOU MADE ABOUT
IDAHO WAS WAY OUT OF LINE,
DO YOU KNOW? AND I WILL--

27:53.873 --> 27:56.042
WILL WHAT?

27:56.075 --> 27:58.410
BEND MY DOG TAGS
AND SEND ME TO VIETNAM?

27:58.444 --> 28:00.880
MY BOSS WAS UNHAPPY.

28:00.913 --> 28:03.750
AND WHEN HE'S UNHAPPY,
HE SPREADS IT AROUND.

28:03.783 --> 28:06.252
YOU GUYS BLOW
THIS OPERATION IN L.A.,

28:06.285 --> 28:10.156
AND I'M GONNA BE THERE
TO JAM IT IN YOU SO DEEP...

28:10.189 --> 28:12.825
YOU'RE GONNA TASTE IT
IN THE BACK OF YOUR THROAT.

28:12.859 --> 28:15.728
I AIN'T YOUR
SECRETARY, BUBBA.

28:15.762 --> 28:18.931
SAVE IT FOR SOMEBODY
THAT'S IMPRESSED.

28:20.800 --> 28:22.935
WE'LL SEE.

28:28.307 --> 28:30.843
WE'LL SEE.

28:30.877 --> 28:32.879
SEE YOU AROUND
THE FLAGPOLE, RYAN.

28:44.156 --> 28:46.092
YOU COME HERE OFTEN,
SAILOR?

28:49.829 --> 28:52.298
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

28:52.331 --> 28:55.601
I GOT YOUR INVITATION.
INVITATION?

28:55.634 --> 28:59.705
YEAH. DIDN'T YOU SET
THINGS UP SO THAT
WE'D HAVE A FEW DAYS FREE?

28:59.738 --> 29:01.841
I--

29:03.843 --> 29:05.945
ROOM 453.

29:20.592 --> 29:22.694
USED TO BE MILITARY?

29:23.863 --> 29:26.265
I MIGHT MAKE
THE SAME QUERY OF YOU.

29:27.834 --> 29:30.903
GETS YOU
OUT OF THE HOUSE.

29:30.937 --> 29:34.841
SO HOMELIFE IS NOT
EXACTLY TO YOUR TASTES?

29:34.874 --> 29:38.077
YOU GOTTA SWING YOUR ARMS
EVERY NOW AND AGAIN.
YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN?

29:38.110 --> 29:41.180
[ Chuckles ]

29:41.213 --> 29:45.151
I WAS AFFLICTED ONCE MYSELF
WITH, UH, HOMELIFE.

29:45.184 --> 29:47.519
BUT I QUICKLY REMEDIED
THAT SITUATION.

29:47.553 --> 29:50.356
[ Laughing ]

29:50.389 --> 29:54.193
SERGEANT, YOU MAY CONTINUE
YOUR ROUNDS NOW.

29:54.226 --> 29:56.362
[ Chuckling ]
YES, SIR.

30:01.200 --> 30:03.135
[ Door Closes ]

30:06.505 --> 30:10.442
NOW TELL ME.
WHO ARE YOU EXACTLY?

30:10.476 --> 30:13.980
AND WHY DO YOU SHOW UP HERE
ON THIS OF ALL DAYS?

30:16.248 --> 30:18.550
I WAS LOST, MAJOR.
I GOT HURT.

30:19.818 --> 30:22.989
[ Screaming ]

30:23.022 --> 30:25.824
[ Continues Screaming ]

30:25.858 --> 30:28.460
THE TRUTH.
IT'S ALREADY BROKE!

30:28.494 --> 30:30.362
THE TRUTH,
OR THAT'S JUST A START.

30:30.396 --> 30:33.065
I-- I WAS HUNTING.

30:33.099 --> 30:34.967
GIVE ME YOUR SERIAL NUMBER.

30:35.001 --> 30:37.736
WHY?
[ Shouts ]

30:37.769 --> 30:39.805
ARE YOU FOR REAL?

30:39.838 --> 30:42.308
WHY IN THE HELL
ARE YOU HESITATING?

30:42.341 --> 30:45.844
- I GOT
A DISHONORABLE DISCHARGE!
- DID YOU INDEED?

30:45.878 --> 30:50.049
- YES, SIR. I DID!
- GIVE ME YOUR SERIAL NUMBER!

30:50.082 --> 30:52.184
MAJOR, I'M JUST A FELLA
WHO WAS HUNTING
ON YOUR MOUNTAIN,

30:52.218 --> 30:56.088
BROKE HIS SHOULDER, AND--
[ Screaming ]

30:56.122 --> 30:59.191
GIVE ME YOUR SERIAL NUMBER
OR I WILL SHOOT.

30:59.225 --> 31:03.462
RA-3--
24341924.

31:05.797 --> 31:09.068
YOU MOVE FROM THIS POSITION,
I WILL KILL YOU.

31:10.036 --> 31:12.071
[ Screaming ]

31:12.104 --> 31:15.707
YOU-- YOU DIDN'T
HAVE TO DO THAT.

31:17.243 --> 31:20.379
[ Groaning ]

31:24.116 --> 31:27.886
[ Radio Static ]
ROMEO FACTION,
THIS IS EARTHWALKER. OVER.

31:27.920 --> 31:30.189
ROMEO FACTION,
THIS IS EARTHWALKER.

31:30.222 --> 31:32.558
[ Radio Static ]
[ Man On Radio ]
THIS IS ROMEO FACTION.

31:32.591 --> 31:34.593
[ Grunts, Groans ]

31:34.626 --> 31:36.362
WHAT IS THE STATUS
OF PLAN MONGOOSE?

31:36.395 --> 31:39.631
[ Man Speaking Spanish ]

31:42.168 --> 31:44.570
[ Groaning ]
I NEED YOU TO RUN
A SERIAL NUMBER.

31:44.603 --> 31:48.040
RA-24341-NINER,

31:48.074 --> 31:49.976
24--
[ Floorboard Creaks ]

31:55.447 --> 31:56.782
HOLD STILL.
REPEAT, HOLD STILL.

31:56.815 --> 31:59.485
[ Man Speaking Spanish ]

31:59.518 --> 32:01.787
[ Static ]

32:04.790 --> 32:07.126
DOG PATCH,
THIS IS DIRT DIVER.

32:07.159 --> 32:10.229
- DOG PATCH, THIS IS
DIRT DIVER. OVER.
- GO AHEAD, DIVER.

32:10.262 --> 32:14.333
TAKE A BACK SHOT OF
THE LOCATION AND TRANSMISSIONS
WITH THE FOLLOWING FREQUENCY.

32:14.366 --> 32:17.436
THE FIRST LOCATION
IS THE SAME AS MY PRESENT.

32:17.469 --> 32:19.505
THE SECOND IS THE ONE
WE ARE SEARCHING FOR.

32:19.538 --> 32:21.740
THAT FREQUENCY IS...

32:21.773 --> 32:25.944
120.362.

32:25.978 --> 32:28.680
GET A LOCATION AND PASS
THAT INFORMATION ON TO
SNAKE DOCTOR IN LOS ANGELES.

32:28.714 --> 32:30.782
ROGER, DIRT DIVER.
TRANSPORT'S ON THE WAY.

32:30.816 --> 32:34.120
MONGOOSE IS IN CUSTODY.
I SAY AGAIN,

32:34.153 --> 32:36.522
MONGOOSE IS IN CUSTODY.

32:44.830 --> 32:48.600
RADIO TRANSMISSIONS
HAVE A LOCATION DOWN
TO ABOUT A MILE FROM HERE.

32:48.634 --> 32:51.137
ANY IDEA IF
THE NEIGHBORHOOD'S UNDER
THE INFLUENCE OF THESE PEOPLE?

32:51.170 --> 32:55.041
UNKNOWN. THAT'S WHY GREY'S
GOT HIS SOCCER SHOES ON.
GAME ON.

32:56.208 --> 32:59.245
[ Train Whistle Blowing ]

33:06.318 --> 33:09.088
[ Men Speaking Spanish ]
* [ Ranchero ]

33:15.761 --> 33:17.696
[ Grey Speaking Spanish ]

33:25.204 --> 33:27.539
[ Grey ]
YOU GOT TWO LARGE
WOODEN DOORS.

33:27.573 --> 33:29.841
OPENINGS ARE BARBWIRED.

33:29.875 --> 33:33.245
WEAPON HOLES
UP THE FRONT.

33:33.279 --> 33:37.049
- THEY LOOK READY FOR A FIGHT.
- THEY MAY BE READY FOR ONE,
BUT THEY DON'T WANT THIS ONE.

33:37.083 --> 33:40.886
PRESIDENT'S GIVEN US
THE GREEN LIGHT.
HOW ARE WE GONNA DO THIS?

33:40.919 --> 33:42.854
I DON'T SEE THIS
TURNING SUBTLE.

33:45.023 --> 33:47.826
WE'RE GONNA NEED
A FIVE-TON FLATBED TRUCK.
ROGER.

33:47.859 --> 33:49.561
AND THE GUY
FROM THE POWER COMPANY.

34:05.977 --> 34:08.414
THE DANGER
YOU PUT ME IN--

34:08.447 --> 34:12.218
THIS TOWN--
THIS HOTEL IS FILLED
WITH PEOPLE WHO KNOW ME.

34:12.251 --> 34:14.453
YOU SENT FOR ME, TOM.

34:14.486 --> 34:17.689
- YOU'RE THE ONE ORDERED MACK
AWAY SO I'D JOIN YOU HERE.
- WHAT?

34:17.723 --> 34:21.093
MACK AND I HAD PLANNED
A WEEKEND, AND YOU ORDERED
HIM TO GO AWAY HUNTING?

34:21.127 --> 34:23.195
TO TAKE SOME TIME OFF?

34:23.229 --> 34:27.233
HE'S ON A MISSION,
TIFFY. HE'S WORKING.

34:32.671 --> 34:34.940
HE'S ALWAYS ON A MISSION.
ISN'T THAT YOUR POINT?

34:34.973 --> 34:38.076
- ISN'T THAT
HOW WE ARRANGE THIS--
- WHY DID YOU COME HERE, TIFFY?

34:41.613 --> 34:43.482
WHERE IS HE?

34:47.653 --> 34:49.521
[ Sighs ]

34:52.824 --> 34:54.960
DON'T I DESERVE
TO KNOW WHERE?

35:01.200 --> 35:03.335
HE'S ON A MISSION.

35:04.303 --> 35:06.338
HE SUCCEEDED.
HE'S SAFE.

35:06.372 --> 35:08.707
HE'LL BE BACK
AT THE BASE TOMORROW.

35:11.009 --> 35:13.179
WAS THE MISSION DANGEROUS?

35:14.146 --> 35:16.148
YES.

35:20.852 --> 35:23.489
AS DANGEROUS AS
THIS IS FOR YOU, TOM?

35:28.059 --> 35:30.696
IS THIS DANGEROUS
ENOUGH FOR YOU?

35:42.874 --> 35:45.511
[ Women Chattering ]

35:45.544 --> 35:48.146
CYNTHIA WANTS TO
TEAR THIS PLACE DOWN
BY RAIDING THE UNIT.

35:48.180 --> 35:49.948
THAT'S NOT WHAT
SHE'S TRYING TO DO.

35:49.981 --> 35:52.818
ARE YOU GONNA RECOMMEND
YOUR HUSBAND TAKE A JOB
WITH THEM?

35:52.851 --> 35:56.288
- OF COURSE NOT.
- WELL, I AM. I'M GONNA
TELL RICK WE SHOULD TAKE IT.

35:56.322 --> 35:58.557
YOU WANT HIM FIGHTING
FOR A CORPORATION
INSTEAD OF HIS COUNTRY?

35:58.590 --> 36:00.559
WHAT DO YOU THINK
THEY'RE FIGHTING FOR IN IRAQ?

36:00.592 --> 36:04.396
WHEN HE WAS IN AFGHANISTAN, I
HAD TO GO ON FEDERAL ASSISTANCE
TO FEED MY THREE GIRLS.

36:04.430 --> 36:07.065
- IT DOESN'T HAVE
TO BE THAT WAY.
- [ Molly ] SAMANTHA'S RIGHT.

36:07.098 --> 36:09.301
IT'S EMBARRASSING
TO HAVE TO ASK FOR HELP...

36:09.335 --> 36:12.671
FROM A GOVERNMENT
THAT YOUR HUSBAND
RISKS HIS LIFE FOR.

36:12.704 --> 36:15.474
- BUT LEAVING THE UNIT
ISN'T THE SOLUTION.
- WHY NOT?

36:15.507 --> 36:19.711
BECAUSE MOST OF OUR HUSBANDS
AREN'T GOING TO LEAVE
EVEN IF WE ASK THEM TO.

36:19.745 --> 36:22.080
- WE HAVE TO FIND WAYS
TO PROVIDE FOR OURSELVES.
- HOW?

36:22.113 --> 36:26.418
WE ALL HAVE A LITTLE MONEY
SAVED, SQUIRRELED, BURIED.

36:26.452 --> 36:29.020
AM I RIGHT?
ALONE, WHAT ARE WE
GONNA DO WITH IT?

36:29.054 --> 36:31.923
- BUT WHAT IF WE
POOLED IT TOGETHER?
- FOR WHAT?

36:31.957 --> 36:36.262
REAL ESTATE. I SEE TWO,
THREE PROPERTIES A WEEK
IN MY OFFICE...

36:36.295 --> 36:38.330
CRIMINALLY UNDERPRICED.

36:38.364 --> 36:41.066
WE MAKE SOME
MINOR IMPROVEMENTS.
WE FLIP IT.

36:41.099 --> 36:44.069
WE CAN ALL MAKE 20,
30% IN A FEW MONTHS.

36:44.102 --> 36:46.372
I DON'T KNOW.

36:46.405 --> 36:49.074
DOING BUSINESS WITH FRIENDS?
HOW DOES THAT NOT GET MESSY?

36:49.107 --> 36:51.343
WHO WOULD YOU RATHER
DO BUSINESS WITH?
YOUR ENEMIES?

36:51.377 --> 36:54.045
WE ALL HAVE
TO FIND OUT WHAT
WE HAVE A STOMACH FOR.

36:54.079 --> 36:57.716
BUT ARE WE GOING TO LET
OUTSIDERS COME IN
AND PICK US OFF ONE BY ONE?

36:57.749 --> 37:00.952
OR ARE WE GOING TO START
TAKING CARE OF OUR FUTURES?

37:00.986 --> 37:05.491
BECAUSE, LORD KNOWS,
THESE MEN CAN'T LOOK
PAST TODAY WITH A TELESCOPE.

37:09.761 --> 37:12.230
YOU KNOW WHEN TO HIT IT?
YES, SIR.
GLAD TO HELP.

37:12.264 --> 37:14.633
GOOD MAN.

37:14.666 --> 37:16.868
NOW THIS HERE'S
A DIFFERENT KIND OF DRIVING.

37:16.902 --> 37:19.738
I BELIEVE I'LL MANAGE.
OKAY THEN.

37:19.771 --> 37:21.940
PUT ON OUR DANCING SHOES.

37:36.522 --> 37:38.624
[ Speaking Spanish ]

37:56.342 --> 37:58.810
OKAY. NOW.

38:08.019 --> 38:09.888
- [ Gunfire ]
- [ Grunts ]

38:18.464 --> 38:20.499
[ Woman Screams ]

38:24.035 --> 38:26.705
- [ Gunfire ]
- [ Grunts ]

38:26.738 --> 38:28.840
TARGETS ELIMINATED.

38:37.082 --> 38:42.020
[ Man On Radio ]
ROGER. SOUTHBOUND
HARBOR FREEWAY, SOUTH OF--

38:42.053 --> 38:44.523
[ Woman On Radio ]
REGARDING SOUTHBOUND
HARBOR FREEWAY--

38:44.556 --> 38:46.892
SERGEANT.

38:46.925 --> 38:50.896
SERGEANT, IT MAY NOT BE
AS VALUABLE AS YOURS,

38:50.929 --> 38:53.599
BUT I WOULD LIKE
FOR YOU TO HAVE MY CARD.

39:14.352 --> 39:16.888
YOU LOST ME HERE.
UH--

39:16.922 --> 39:18.990
I WANT TO BUY
THE ARMORY PROPERTY.
WHAT?

39:19.024 --> 39:22.227
MY FRIENDS AND ME,
WE'RE PREPARED
TO OFFER FULL PRICE.

39:22.260 --> 39:24.095
THE PRICE JUST GOT RAISED.

39:24.129 --> 39:25.997
LARRY SAID YOU THOUGHT
WE UNDERPRICED IT.

39:26.031 --> 39:28.900
ALL RIGHT.
HOW MUCH MORE?

39:30.436 --> 39:32.438
$20,000 MORE?
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN?

39:32.471 --> 39:35.607
WE NEED TO COME UP
WITH $4,000 MORE
FOR A DOWN PAYMENT.

39:35.641 --> 39:37.509
IT MEANS A BIGGER LOAN.
IT MEANS--

39:37.543 --> 39:40.579
IS IT
STILL A BARGAIN?
YES.

39:40.612 --> 39:43.214
CAN WE STILL MAKE MONEY?
YES, BUT--

39:43.248 --> 39:45.751
BUT WHAT?
IS IT A GOOD RISK?

39:46.785 --> 39:48.787
YES, IT IS.

39:48.820 --> 39:52.190
WHAT ARE WE AFRAID OF?
FACING OUR HUSBANDS?

39:52.223 --> 39:54.893
SAYING WE LOST SOME MONEY
TRYING TO BETTER OURSELVES?

39:54.926 --> 39:58.296
WHAT WE'RE REALLY TALKING
ABOUT HERE IS RISK.

39:58.329 --> 40:02.100
ISN'T THAT
WHAT OUR HUSBANDS DO
WHEN THEY GO TO WORK?

40:02.133 --> 40:04.436
ISN'T THAT WHAT WE DO
EVERY TIME WE SEND THEM OUT?

40:05.571 --> 40:08.039
THIS IS JUST THE SAME THING.

40:08.073 --> 40:10.942
- EXCEPT A LOT CHEAPER
FOR THE PRICE.
- [ Check Rips ]

40:16.114 --> 40:18.016
I'LL TELL HIM
WE'LL TAKE IT.

40:21.587 --> 40:23.889
WHAT IS SHE, LIKE,
SIX INCHES TALLER THAN YOU?
WHOA. WHOA. WHOA.

40:23.922 --> 40:26.157
WE'RE THE SAME HEIGHT
LYING DOWN, BROTHER.

40:26.191 --> 40:29.628
IN THAT CASE, ISN'T SHE
FATTER THAN YOU THEN?
DON'T HATE THE PLAYER.

40:29.661 --> 40:32.430
YOU FEEL IT?
TOP?

40:32.464 --> 40:34.600
OUT THERE WITH THE TEAM--
YOU FEELING IT YET?

40:34.633 --> 40:36.635
STARTING TO.

40:36.668 --> 40:40.171
WHAT'S BETTER THAN IT?
NOTHING.

40:40.205 --> 40:43.441
RIGHT. THEN YOU CAN
STAND DOWN ON YOUR NEED
TO IMPRESS EVERYONE.

40:43.475 --> 40:45.443
ALL DUE RESPECT, SARGE.

40:45.477 --> 40:48.146
I GOTTA START AT SQUARE ONE
EVERY DAY WITH YOU GUYS
TO PROVE MYSELF.

40:48.179 --> 40:50.148
UP AND DOWN.
WELL, THERE'S
SOME TRUTH IN THAT.

40:50.181 --> 40:52.317
AND THE FACT
THAT YOU KNOW IT
IS IMPRESSIVE.

40:52.350 --> 40:54.820
YOU COMING ON TO ME, TOP?

41:09.735 --> 41:13.071
COME OVER HERE,
SERGEANT MAJOR,
AND GIVE ME A REPORT.

41:15.874 --> 41:17.943
[ Sighs ]

41:17.976 --> 41:19.911
HOW WAS THE HUNTING?

41:23.048 --> 41:25.684
I BAGGED A BIG ONE.
[ Chuckles ]

41:26.985 --> 41:29.154
IS THAT SHOULDER
BOTHERING YOU AGAIN,
BABE?

41:29.187 --> 41:32.157
YEAH. I KNOCKED IT
OUT OF JOINT AGAIN.

41:33.692 --> 41:37.162
GOD, MACK, YOU GOTTA
STOP DOING THAT
FOR $10 BAR BETS.

41:42.100 --> 41:44.002
THIS ONE WAS WORTH IT.

41:45.070 --> 41:47.873
HERE. LET ME
MASSAGE IT FOR YOU.

41:57.883 --> 42:00.752
HOW WAS YOUR WEEKEND?

42:01.920 --> 42:04.055
IT WAS QUIET.

42:06.692 --> 42:08.827
NICE TATTOO.

42:08.860 --> 42:11.529
WELL, IT'LL WASH OFF
IN A COUPLE DAYS.

42:11.563 --> 42:14.065
WELL, I KIND OF LIKE IT.

42:17.703 --> 42:20.538
I'M GONNA MAKE
THIS UP TO YOU, TIFFY.

42:23.408 --> 42:26.344
I REALLY WILL.

42:26.377 --> 42:28.246
YOU PROMISE, MACK?

42:30.381 --> 42:32.250
JUST US?

42:34.485 --> 42:37.088
AND REAL SOON?

42:37.122 --> 42:38.990
YOU PROMISE?

42:54.505 --> 42:57.943
[ Call And Response ]
* FIRED UP
FIRED UP *

43:04.415 --> 43:07.152
* TWENTY-SEVEN
FIRED UP *
